[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 8.0,
    "text": "Oh, it's always so nice when my courage brings home new friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 10.0,
    "text": "Such a treat!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "Oh, I'm too pocky!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "Courage, I think the sink's clogged again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "He has such wonderfully small paws. So, I take it you're a travelling band of tinkers, then?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 39.0,
    "text": "Um, not quite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "Although we have been known to tinker around with a mystery or two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "See what I did there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "Nice one, Daph."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.0,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "Nice work, Cookie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.0,
    "endTime": 57.0,
    "text": "We actually drive all over the place solving mysteries."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.0,
    "endTime": 61.0,
    "text": "In a van! Oh, I do so like your caravan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.0,
    "endTime": 63.0,
    "text": "Thanks, I just had it re-decaled."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.0,
    "endTime": 67.0,
    "text": "I wasn't sure at first, but in the end, I went with the flowers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 81.0,
    "text": "So, you're professional riddle-solvers, then?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "Mystery-solvers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "We solve mysteries."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 88.0,
    "text": "You know the deal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.0,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "How nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 92.0,
    "text": "I love riddles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "Do you know this one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "What can travel around the world while staying in a corner?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "A stamp!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 106.0,
    "text": "Getcha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "A post-it stamp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "Always in the corner of the envelope, travelling all over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.0,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "I can't believe I didn't get that. Oh, don't worry, dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "I'm sure you're much smarter than that silly old riddle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.0,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "I've loads more if you want. My dude, man, these Scottish Dream cookies are really, really like extra dreamy, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 133.0,
    "text": "Yeah, Wiggy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "Deliciously dreamy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 137.0,
    "text": "I'm so glad you boys like them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "I've got loads more of those, too, if you're still hungry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "We're always hungry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.0,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "And we love the words loads more, especially when it comes to food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.0,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "Right, Scoop?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "Yeah, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "Food. Hey, dude."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.0,
    "endTime": 165.0,
    "text": "What's wrong, little pink guy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.0,
    "endTime": 176.0,
    "text": "You okay, Curly? My dude!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.0,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "My dude!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "He's one of those crazy monster cicada things on my back!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 186.0,
    "text": "It's just a wee bug, dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.0,
    "endTime": 188.0,
    "text": "Don't fret."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 189.0,
    "text": "I'll get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 193.0,
    "text": "Oh, still dead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.0,
    "endTime": 194.0,
    "text": "Oh, my."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "Daphne, be a dear and open the back door."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 205.0,
    "text": " Oh!"
  }
]